        <item>
            <title>Apple Intelligence 4 月登陸 Apple Vision Pro——visionOS 2.4 推出多項強大功能</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/22/apple-vision-pro-7/vr-mr-ar/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=apple-vision-pro-7</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/22/apple-vision-pro-7/vr-mr-ar/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 22 Feb 2025 06:01:22 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[VR 科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple Vision Pro]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1293516</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p data-start="74" data-end="346">Apple 宣佈 Apple Intelligence 將於 4 月正式登陸 Apple Vision Pro，為空間計算帶來更高層次的人工智能應用。新功能包括「書寫工具」支援文字修改與 ChatGPT 整合、「影像樂園」提供 AI 生成影像創作，以及 Genmoji 讓用户創作個人化表情符號。此外 visionOS 2.4 亦推出全新「Spatial Gallery」app，帶來藝術與娛樂內容體驗；iPhone 版「Apple Vision Pro」app 亦同步登場，讓用户可透過 iPhone 管理 Vision Pro 應用與設定。</p><p data-start="74" data-end="346"><p data-start="74" data-end="346"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293523" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/vlcsnap2025022213h57-4-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/vlcsnap2025022213h57-4-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/vlcsnap2025022213h57-4.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p data-start="74" data-end="346"><h2 data-start="348" data-end="394"><strong data-start="353" data-end="394">Apple Intelligence 強化 Vision Pro 使用體驗</strong></h2><p data-start="396" data-end="585">Apple Intelligence 為 Vision Pro 帶來多項 AI 功能，提升生產力與創造力。「書寫工具」讓用户能夠在「郵件」、「備忘錄」及其他應用中重寫、校對與撮寫文字，甚至利用 ChatGPT 從零開始生成內容。透過「重寫」功能，用户可調整語氣，使文字更專業、友好或簡潔，而「校對」則可檢查文法並提供修改建議。「撮寫」功能可將選取文字轉換為不同格式的摘要。</p><p data-start="396" data-end="585"><p data-start="396" data-end="585"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293518" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/applevisionos24apple-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/applevisionos24apple-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/applevisionos24apple-1-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p data-start="396" data-end="585"><p data-start="587" data-end="699">「影像樂園」則讓 Vision Pro 用户以 AI 創建獨特影像，根據輸入的描述生成相應畫面，甚至可透過個人相片庫創作與家人或朋友相似的影像。這項功能整合至「訊息」與「Freeform」等應用，也可作為獨立 app 使用。</p><p data-start="587" data-end="699"><p data-start="587" data-end="699"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293525" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/vlcsnap2025022213h56-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/vlcsnap2025022213h56-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/vlcsnap2025022213h56-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p data-start="587" data-end="699"><p data-start="701" data-end="797">Genmoji 讓用户能透過 AI 創造個人化表情符號，這些 Genmoji 可嵌入訊息、轉換為貼圖，或用於「點按回應」。而「智慧型回覆」功能則能根據訊息內容提供建議回覆，提升溝通效率。</p><p data-start="701" data-end="797"><p data-start="701" data-end="797"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293524" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/vlcsnap2025022213h56-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/vlcsnap2025022213h56-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/vlcsnap2025022213h56.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p data-start="701" data-end="797"><h2 data-start="799" data-end="825"><strong data-start="804" data-end="825">「製作回憶影片」與 AI 搜尋相片</strong></h2><p data-start="827" data-end="958">Apple Intelligence 亦強化「相片」app，透過「製作回憶影片」功能，用户只需輸入簡單描述，AI 便會從相片庫中挑選最適合的影像與影片，組成具故事性的影片，並搭配音樂。「自然語言搜尋」功能允許用户以簡單描述搜尋特定相片或影片，無需手動篩選。</p><p data-start="827" data-end="958"><p data-start="827" data-end="958"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293520" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/vlcsnap2025022213h57-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/vlcsnap2025022213h57-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/vlcsnap2025022213h57-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p data-start="827" data-end="958"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293519" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/vlcsnap2025022213h57-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/vlcsnap2025022213h57-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/vlcsnap2025022213h57.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/22/apple-vision-pro-7/vr-mr-ar/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
