        <item>
            <title>【開箱】《人中之龍 8 外傳，夏威夷海盜》收藏盒限定版，真島吾朗毒蛇眼罩超型</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/22/like-a-dragon-2/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=like-a-dragon-2</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/22/like-a-dragon-2/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Gary Lee]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 22 Feb 2025 03:59:48 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[遊戲情報]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1293488</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>《人中之龍 8 外傳，夏威夷海盜》剛剛發售，小編也取得了中文收藏盒限定版，立即同大家開箱看看。</p><p><a title="_DSC7527" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54342942775/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54342942775_29a3c1e157_b.jpg" alt="_DSC7527" width="1024" height="683" /></a></p><h2>今集外傳玩什麼？</h2><p>《人中之龍 8 外傳，夏威夷海盜》是《人中之龍》系列的外傳作品，以系列經典角色真島吾朗為主角，故事設定在《人中之龍 8》事件結束後的半年，真島吾朗在一場船難後漂流至一個名為裏奇島的偏遠小島，醒來時發現自己失去了記憶，甚至連名字都無法想起。在少年諾亞·裏奇的救助下，真島開始尋找記憶的線索，並意外捲入一場圍繞失落寶藏的冒險。為了找回過去並揭開隱藏的真相，他組建了自己的海盜團，駕駛名為「吾朗丸」的海盜船，航向浩瀚的大海，展開一場驚心動魄的旅程。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293493" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/072-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/072-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/072.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293495" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/022-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/022-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/022.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>遊戲的核心玩法延續了《人中之龍》系列的動作冒險傳統，並加入了海盜主題的創新元素，讓玩家體驗陸地與海洋雙重戰場的樂趣。真島吾朗擁有兩種獨特的戰鬥風格，玩家可根據戰況自由切換：</p><p>狂犬風格：延續真島在系列中的經典形象，以短刀和敏捷的身手進行高速單體攻擊，適合應對強敵。這個風格結合拳擊、踢擊和刀擊，可發動空中連擊，並使用「瘋狂計量表」召喚分身進行組合攻擊，效果華麗且強大。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293492" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/032-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/032-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/032.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293496" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/071-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/071-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/071.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>海盜風格：融入海盜元素，使用雙持彎刀進行大範圍羣攻，並能運用三種側武器：彎刀迴旋鏢，手槍，鏈鈎。此外，海盜風格還能使用「黑暗樂器」召喚黑暗神祇，例如小提琴召喚食人鯊、薩克斯風召喚鳥類龍捲風、吉他召喚巨猿、陶笛召喚治癒與控制敵人的水母，這些神祇的召喚效果依敵人數量或戰場環境而變化。戰鬥中還有熱行動，在特定條件下發動強力攻擊，增加戰鬥的策略性和爽快感。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293491" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/021-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/021-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/021.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293494" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/041-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/041-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/041.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>駕駛吾朗丸海戰</h2><p>遊戲的一大亮點是玩家可以駕駛「吾朗丸」進行海上探索與戰鬥。玩家可以操控船隻進行炮擊，需避開敵方火力，並可使用火箭發射器攻擊。船隻可通過升級強化甲板、添加火焰噴射器或雷射，增加戰鬥能力。亦設有登船戰，在削弱敵船後，玩家可登船進行近身戰鬥，利用真島的能力和船員支援。船員可提供攻擊或治療效果，玩家可招募超過 100 位船員，這些船員可在夏威夷和馬德蘭蒂斯周圍招募。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293497" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/14-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/14-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/14.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293498" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/042-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/042-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/042.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><br /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293499" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/031-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/031-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/031.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>收藏盒限定版開箱</h2><p><a title="_DSC7529" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54342742174/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54342742174_7ef1e450f2_b.jpg" alt="_DSC7529" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><h2>超型毒蛇眼罩</h2><p>限定版幾年精品中，小編最為喜愛這件了，印刷精莫的修羅面具盒子內，就是裝有皮革製的真島吾朗毒蛇眼罩，最正的是有條立體的銀色毒蛇，又型又靚，當作是 Cosplay 道具應該也非常不錯，相信 Fans 看到實物應該也會超喜愛的。</p><p><a title="_DSC7533" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54342758458/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54342758458_dbc1bc1f17_b.jpg" alt="_DSC7533" width="1024" height="683" /></a></p><p><a title="_DSC7536" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54341629947/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54341629947_9344005ddd_b.jpg" alt="_DSC7536" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><h2>插到真島吾朗彈出來多人玩具</h2><p>這個名為真島吾朗「危機一發」派對多人玩具，是由玩具廠 Takara Tomy 製作的，可以多人輪流插膠刀仔入木桶，看誰會插到 Q 版真島吾朗彈出來。</p><p><a title="_DSC7542" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54342942720/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54342942720_ec7bfa88fa_b.jpg" alt="_DSC7542" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><br /><a title="_DSC7543" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54342758398/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54342758398_5a4bd77f02_b.jpg" alt="_DSC7543" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="_DSC7548" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54342529571/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54342529571_b75e740432_b.jpg" alt="_DSC7548" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><h2>真島吾朗海盜亞加力直立牌</h2><p>這是一個 A4 Size 的亞加力膠直立牌，那張畫正是遊戲盒圖那張真島吾朗海盜畫像。</p><h2><a title="_DSC7561" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54342529561/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54342529561_ea22bc8485_b.jpg" alt="_DSC7561" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></h2><h2>DLC 序號各種組合包</h2><p>1. 傳説海盜船員組合包（能夠將桐生一馬和堂島大吾等系列人氣角色新增為吾朗海盜團船員）<br />
2. 傳説穿搭組合包（能夠讓主角真島換上桐生一馬和冴島大河等歷代系列人氣角色服裝，以及本作原創 T-shirt ）<br />
3. 吾朗丸特別自訂組合包（能夠變更海盜船 「吾朗丸」 外觀的零件套組。以桐生一馬和春日一番等人氣角色為主題設計）<br />
4. 追加卡拉 OK 樂曲 &amp; BGM 組合包（可在卡拉 OK 新增曲目以外，還能獲得將人氣歌曲當作行走時背景音樂的道具）</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293489" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mwtmzvv1_mpwxov8ywwp-694x505.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="505" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mwtmzvv1_mpwxov8ywwp-694x505.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mwtmzvv1_mpwxov8ywwp.jpg 1236w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/02/22/like-a-dragon-2/game-channel/">【開箱】《人中之龍 8 外傳，夏威夷海盜》收藏盒限定版，真島吾朗毒蛇眼罩超型</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
